st. Photograph: Martin Christopher/Alamy","width":"140"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Travel/Pix/pictures/2013/6/12/1371052002445/Southwestern-style-bowl-o-003.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Alamy","altText":"Southwestern style bowl of green and red chili peppers on a rustic wood background.","height":"84","credit":"Alamy","caption":"Mexican food cliche alert … it's not all about the red and the green. Ask a Mexican has some Tex-Mex alternatives to suggest. Photograph: Martin Christopher/Alamy","width":"140"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Travel/Pix/pictures/2013/6/12/1371052003575/Southwestern-style-bowl-o-004.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Alamy","altText":"Southwestern style bowl of green and red chili peppers on a rustic wood background.","height":"132","credit":"Alamy","caption":"Mexican food cliche alert … it's not all about the red and the green. Ask a Mexican has some Tex-Mex alternatives to suggest. Photograph: Martin Christopher/Alamy","width":"220"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Travel/Pix/pictures/2013/6/12/1371052004755/Southwestern-style-bowl-o-005.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Alamy","altText":"Southwestern style bowl of green and red chili peppers on a rustic wood background.","height":"168","credit":"Alamy","caption":"Mexican food cliche alert … it's not all about the red and the green. Ask a Mexican has some Tex-Mex alternatives to suggest. Photograph: Martin Christopher/Alamy","width":"280"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Travel/Pix/pictures/2013/6/12/1371052005889/Southwestern-style-bowl-o-006.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Alamy","altText":"Southwestern style bowl of green and red chili peppers on a rustic wood background.","height":"180","credit":"Alamy","caption":"Mexican food cliche alert … it's not all about the red and the green. Ask a Mex